    {
      "id": "theme-state-grammar-findings",
      "type": "markdown",
      "label": "First-Pass Loudness Findings",
      "position": {
        "x": 420,
        "y": 620
      },
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "width": 520,
      "height": 380,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "# First-Pass Loudness Findings\n\n## Loudest accidental offenders\n\n1. **Ports / handles**\n- full saturated blue/green circles at all times\n- white outlines even at rest\n- hover and drag add dark shadow + size jump\n- hit area is huge, which is good for usability but makes the visual grammar feel widget-heavy\n\n2. **Edge labels**\n- hard black text on white boxes with black borders\n- large bold default font\n- reads louder than the edges they annotate\n\n3. **Edges in active states**\n- hover / selection / glow use strong shadow and animation quickly\n- this can overpower the node surfaces instead of supporting them\n\n4. **Global accent usage**\n- theme defaults still lean on strong primary / secondary values\n- there is no calm token layer between theme palette and component styling\n\n5. **Typography baseline**\n- global font is still `Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif`\n- this is not just a taste problem; it makes the visual system feel accidental\n\n## Audit conclusion\nThe app is currently loud by direct component styling, not by a shared state grammar.\n\nThe next move is not random color tuning. It is:\n- define calm hover/active/focus tokens\n- make ports and labels consume those tokens first\n- then reduce one-off shadows, outlines, and hardcoded contrast",
        "_classBinding": {
          "key": "markdown",
          "sourceRef": "/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
          "ref": "/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
          "identity": {
            "graphId": "markdown_class",
            "name": "markdown Node Class",
            "version": "0.1.0",
            "description": "Canonical markdown content node.",
            "createdAt": "2026-02-24T20:05:15Z",
            "updatedAt": "2026-03-24T01:20:00.000Z"
          },
          "intent": "graph",
          "meaning": "Canonical markdown content node.",
          "description": "Canonical markdown content node.",
          "defaults": {},
          "nodeDef": {
            "key": "markdown",
            "ref": "/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
            "source": "local",
            "version": ">=0.1.0"
          },
          "views": [
            {
              "key": "markdown",
              "intent": "editor",
              "payload": "editor.web",
              "ref": "/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
              "source": "local",
              "version": ">=0.1.0"
            },
            {
              "key": "markdown",
              "intent": "node",
              "payload": "node.web",
              "ref": "/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
              "source": "local",
              "version": ">=0.1.0"
            }
          ],
          "nodeView": {
            "key": "markdown",
            "intent": "node",
            "payload": "node.web",
            "ref": "/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
            "source": "local",
            "version": ">=0.1.0"
          },
          "editorView": {
